{"tid":1389112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【分析】天水圍放煙花係一場傑出PR","createTime":"2019-07-30T22:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T23:09:13.000Z","uid":197404,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc02f7fc030a66efbd66c49aa2d61fefc121793","tid":1389112,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:45:40.000Z","msg":"【分析】天水圍放煙花係一場傑出PR<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389037</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n之前位巴打po左係吹水台無乜人睇<br />\n我重新po一次係時事台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由千夫所指到主持大局</span><br />\n抗議者包圍警署，原本警察只能被動地被圍屌。但當外面馬路突然放煙花，然後即刻有個外表上鏡、似足TVB警察劇主角既藍衫出黎講野，呼籲救人要緊。<br />\n放煙花之後，抗議者由抗議警察執法不公，變成市民尋求警察保護。放煙花之後，現場由抗議警權，係「救人要緊」既大旗下，急速逆轉成由警察「主持大局」，甚至因此得到掌聲。「執法不公」、拘捕學生時「濫用暴力」、「警黑合作」完全被放埋一邊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時間天衣無縫</span><br />\n放煙花時間，剛好安排在3位學生被釋放之後數分鐘；「驅散人群」的觀感大減，始終釋放學生就，追究執法不公的關注度就會降低。然後一放煙花，「救人要緊」就自然完全蓋過追究執法不公。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一洗落閘「唔做野」形象</span><br />\n天水圍警署比人屌得最勁，就係7.21落閘唔做野。但今次一反常態地，幾個警察即刻衝出黎「執法」。趁抗議者同記者齊哂人，係鏡頭面前高調「做野」，一洗「唔做野」既形象。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">帶領輿論，追究警黑合作</span><br />\n假車牌、玩煙花、南亞人；事件明顯係有組織既行動。究竟乜野人策劃？放煙花對乜野人最有利？只要扣連係警黑合作既脈絡下思考，答案根本好明顯。但我地需要既，係將依件事分析比大眾知道，唔可以比「民意翻盤」依件事發生。"},{"pid":"43229f296d6609e5b35681b97c7c348cbd15d9d5","tid":1389112,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:47:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdf00290205c58f7dbb39255368ba80fc1ce93ee","tid":1389112,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:47:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16e7431785006eb27d8120d801fcbe5060b0af8d","tid":1389112,"uid":248182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faad2363a4510f014d9d8888213b9088f73a1e4","tid":1389112,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:51:06.000Z","msg":"同埋夜晚帶風向問題真係好嚴重<br />\n葵涌有人拎真槍既po已經完全見唔到<br />\n<br />\n(突然諗到)致勝關鍵「撐警大行動」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389001</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n仲有d p牌新po係到講埋要一齊撐警<br />\n明明比人屌完話放棄<br />\n但又係到瘋狂推po<br />\n<br />\n諗起之前都有狗係到扮連儂牆南亞人既fd攞料<br />\n班夜更mon po狗除左mon po仲係到周圍開新ac帶風向<br />\n佢地係咪晚晚開一次會傾個晚要帶咩風既？"},{"pid":"6bde4210696fae396a9ca36e57ff48d31e45dc95","tid":1389112,"uid":259321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZ4DuJN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZ4DuJN.gif&h=747f5fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【攪珠遊擊戰】攪珠系統 (公測版 v1.0) 上線喇!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全港18區警署轉轉盤上線喇!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388648</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9e6b03383ffc8096186a9d82c2da1cc8c8c43637","tid":1389112,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:54:04.000Z","msg":"有無辦法防到班it狗咁樣洗走d有用po<br />\n得翻無用po上熱門"},{"pid":"215f972eb0acec4a3da8c6d6976a72afe18a780e","tid":1389112,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491e725e1a564e819ad7eb35d24c2dca127a5e2a","tid":1389112,"uid":274294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:55:04.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777ed622093c330b05b20cf201c3e4cf2d4f7415","tid":1389112,"uid":197404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:56:26.000Z","msg":"不要說推<br />\n試著說5/8罷工"},{"pid":"ffd4f8b6af904467719a80d56a9bf7408521c1af","tid":1389112,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121c3a56cff0b00c2e8f1ba5f9b69da60b019dbd","tid":1389112,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:03:15.000Z","msg":"原來有巴打整合曬佢地既策略<br />\n推佢嗰個<br />\n<br />\n全部人推聲援,葵芳出真槍同打記者,天水圍煙花post, 天水圍的PR對與錯就由佢沉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba6853a35bbc51791cbdc82e49540e4e1094ae5b","tid":1389112,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:09:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}